<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Blog by 빡기]]></title><description><![CDATA[Blog by 빡기]]></description><link>https://pgs787.github.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2020 05:28:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[(1/29) Wecode study 2일차]]></title><description><![CDATA[JavaScript 정리]]></description><link>https://pgs787.github.io/pages/posts//posts/blog-tags/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://pgs787.github.io/pages/posts//posts/blog-tags/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2020 23:41:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#javascript%EB%9E%80&quot;&gt;JavaScript란?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95&quot;&gt;특징&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;javascript란&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#javascript%EB%9E%80&quot; aria-label=&quot;javascript란 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;JavaScript란?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;넷스케이프 커뮤니케이션즈사(Netscape Communications)가 개발한 스크립트 언어&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;웹을 풍부하게 만들어주는 작고 가벼운 언어&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;객체 지향 언어&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;변수 자료형을 선언하지 않아 동적임&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;인터프리터식 해석&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;특징&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95&quot; aria-label=&quot;특징 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;특징&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;String + Number를 하는 경우 무조건 String으로 강제 형변환&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;전위(++num) vs 후위(num++) 증감 연산자 &lt;u&gt;!! 할당순서의 차이 !!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;num++
변수에 먼저 값을 할당 한 뒤 증감
++num
숫자를 먼저 증감한 뒤 변수에 할당&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;함수선언식-vs-함수표현식-u호이스팅의-영향-u&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%EC%8B%9D-vs-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84%EC%8B%9D-u%ED%98%B8%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85%EC%9D%98-%EC%98%81%ED%96%A5-u&quot; aria-label=&quot;함수선언식 vs 함수표현식 u호이스팅의 영향 u permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;함수선언식 vs 함수표현식 &lt;u&gt;호이스팅의 영향 !!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;자바스크립트는 기본적으로 ES6에 추가 된 변수형인 let,const도 호이스팅에 영향을 안준다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;함수선언식은 호이스팅이 되는 반면에 함수표현식은 호이스팅에 영향을 안 받는다&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;즉, var형태를 제외하고 나머지(함수 표현식 제외)는 전부 호이스팅 영향을 받지 않음!!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;호이스팅이란&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%ED%98%B8%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80&quot; aria-label=&quot;호이스팅이란 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;호이스팅이란❔&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;브라우저가 위치와 관계없이 js를 해석할때 맨위로 끌어 올리는 행위&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;일반-함수-vs-화살표-함수-uthis의-차이-u&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%EC%9D%BC%EB%B0%98-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-vs-%ED%99%94%EC%82%B4%ED%91%9C-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-uthis%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4-u&quot; aria-label=&quot;일반 함수 vs 화살표 함수 uthis의 차이 u permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;일반 함수 vs 화살표 함수 &lt;u&gt;this의 차이 !!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;클로저처럼 내부메소드가 감싸져있는 함수의 변수를 가리키는 것&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[(1/28) Wecode study 1일차]]></title><description><![CDATA[HTML CSS 정리]]></description><link>https://pgs787.github.io/pages/posts//posts/blog-tags/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://pgs787.github.io/pages/posts//posts/blog-tags/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2020 23:41:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#htmlhyper-text-markup-language%EB%9E%80&quot;&gt;HTML이란?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#csscascading-style-sheets%EB%9E%80&quot;&gt;CSS란?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;htmlhyper-text-markup-language란&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#htmlhyper-text-markup-language%EB%9E%80&quot; aria-label=&quot;htmlhyper text markup language란 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;HTML(Hyper Text Markup Language)란?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;웹 페이지를 만들기 위한 언어&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;다양한 태그들로 구성 (a, span, div, header, body)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;브라우저가 태그 및 속성들을 이해하고 사용자에게 보여줌&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;tag-간단-정리&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#tag-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC&quot; aria-label=&quot;tag 간단 정리 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Tag 간단 정리&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!DOCTYPE&amp;gt; - HTML을 나타내는 태그, 제일 첫줄에 위치, HTML 5버전 사용 의미
&amp;lt;head&amp;gt; - 사이트의 제목, 부가 설명 등 meta, title이 들어감
&amp;lt;body&amp;gt; - HTML의 본문 역할, 화면에 보여지는 내용
&amp;lt;h1&amp;gt;,&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt; - 중요 내용 글씨 크기 설정
&amp;lt;span&amp;gt; - 한 줄로 나오는 텍스트, 개행 x
&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; - 한 단락으로 구성, 개행 o
&amp;lt;a&amp;gt; - 하이퍼 링크, 클릭시 사이트로 이동
&amp;lt;div&amp;gt; - html에서 사용도가 높은 태그&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;www.w3schools.com&quot; title=&quot;w3school.com&quot;&gt;Tag 정리 사이트 참조!!!!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;block-level-element-vs-inline-element&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#block-level-element-vs-inline-element&quot; aria-label=&quot;block level element vs inline element permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Block Level Element vs inline Element&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Block Level Element - div, form, p&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;기본적으로 개행이 이루어짐&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;한줄로 이루어지며 좌우 폭이 최대로 맞춰짐&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;inline Element - span, a, p&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;단락의 흐름을 방해하지 않음&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;개행이 이루어지지 않음&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;display, inline 속성을 이용하면 아래와 같이 수정 가능&lt;br&gt;
block =&gt; inline&lt;br&gt;
inline =&gt; block&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;csscascading-style-sheets란&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#csscascading-style-sheets%EB%9E%80&quot; aria-label=&quot;csscascading style sheets란 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;CSS(Cascading Style Sheets)란?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HTML이 정보를 표현한다면 CSS는 HTML을 시각적으로 꾸며주는 역할&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;끌꼴이나 배경 너비 및 위치를 조정하거나 뼈대를 꾸며주는 중요한 역할&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;브라우저별로 태그마다 기본 css가 있어 reset.css를 이용하면 브라우저 상관없이 초기조건인 0으로 시작 할 수 있다!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;css-선택자&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#css-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90&quot; aria-label=&quot;css 선택자 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;CSS 선택자&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HTML 안에 있는 원하는 요소에 효과를 주고 싶을 때 선택가능하게 해주는 것&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All Selector(전체 선택자)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;- {
  margin: 0 0 0 5px
  }

// 모든 요소를 선택할 시 사용&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type Selector(타입 선택자)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
